Steps:
[NAV] {{BACK_URL}}/ui/graphiql
[WAIT] GraphiQL interface loads
[AUTH] authenticate with Bearer token obtained for {{USER_EMAIL}}
[GQL] enter query: { promotionCoupons(storeId: "{{STORE_ID}}", cultureName: "{{CULTURE_NAME}}", first: 20) { totalCount items { id systemName name description endDate couponCode } } }
[ACT] click 'Execute' (Run button)
[WAIT] query response appears
